title: UNC baseball loses first game of the series to Virginia Tech, falling 12-1 - The Daily Tar Heel
content: UNC baseball loses first game of the series to Virginia Tech, falling 12-1  The Daily Tar Heel
description: In the first game of the weekend series, the No. 18 North Carolina baseball team (19-7, 5-5 ACC) fell to the Virginia Tech Hokies (16-6, 4-4 ACC), 12-1, Friday night at Boshamer Stadium.
